### Carrier list
GET http://localhost/api/carrier

### Carrier detail
GET http://localhost/api/carrier/1

### Carrier create
POST http://localhost/api/carrier
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "carrierName": "Test Carrier",
  "carrierContact": "051-999-9999",
  "managerName": "Test Manager",
  "carrierStatus": "approved"
}

### Carrier update
PUT http://localhost/api/carrier/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "carrierName": "Updated Carrier",
  "carrierContact": "051-888-8888",
  "managerName": "Updated Manager",
  "carrierStatus": "hold"
}

### Carrier delete
DELETE http://localhost/api/carrier/1
